{"tid":2417391,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所研SPAC融資機制 業界不感樂觀：與打擊借殼上市背道而馳","createTime":"2021-02-22T00:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T02:25:40.000Z","uid":50386,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dba7a9cda7562db92b8e4e2e62f2b7a44c427aaa","tid":2417391,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"SPAC熱潮席捲美國新股市場，新加坡交易所亦高調表態，力爭年內引入SPAC機制，欲搶先飲亞洲區「頭啖湯」。近日市場盛傳港交所（388）開始研究SPAC，本報獲悉該所向個別券商了解意見。但有專家認為，引入SPAC機制與港交所收緊借殼上市的原意存在衝突，加上「中概股」回流絡繹不絕，港交所不缺生意。<br />\n<br />\n然而，細價股專家、宏高證券投資經理梁杰文認為，港交所近年嚴打啤殼，期望公司循正常IPO程序上市，SPAC與港交所的原意有衝突，若推SPAC機制無疑是自打嘴巴。他認為，即使該所研究SPAC亦不感意外，只是順應潮流的門面工夫，「香港市場彈性無美股咁大，SPAC牽涉到修改《上市規則》，由諮詢到落實至少消耗幾年時間，屆時SPAC熱潮都可能過咗。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210222/J3NEWVRNCFBGJASTKF5Q2WP37E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210222%2FJ3NEWVRNCFBGJASTKF5Q2WP37E%2F&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=3bb99c86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210222%2FJ3NEWVRNCFBGJASTKF5Q2WP37E%2F&h=3cf7c15d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210222/J3NEWVRNCFBGJASTKF5Q2WP37E/</a>"},{"pid":"bfbcc3de1fdb95f55196f0b8700bc584f76bfeee","tid":2417391,"uid":226902,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:24:56.000Z","msg":"笑撚死人咩 港股所有small cap 咪已經係SPAC 囉 全部殼股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778f0beb8b9ea3af9df0da4ad3dfd0b3148d601b","tid":2417391,"uid":162954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:34:33.000Z","msg":"港交所會有進步 真係笑9大人個口"},{"pid":"7c6dabaa428a0b23f911f1d3812d1207b12d1786","tid":2417391,"uid":169116,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T00:38:17.000Z","msg":"唔駛諗，spac機制去到中國人地方就會變晒做妖股。"},{"pid":"17b8687f5b088f5c74d98ec9f3404f8d814cd8e8","tid":2417391,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,